spec_data.Name: goobook
spec_data.Description:
Goobook is a command-line interface to Google contacts. It includes
* Searching contacts
* Mutt integration (the same way as for abook)
* Adding new contacts (very basic)
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 01:58:54 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Abook-style interface for google contacts for mutt
